Follow AGENTS.md.

Priority order:

1. User goals
2. Usability
3. Information architecture
4. Accessibility
5. Performance
6. Visual design
7. Animation

Do not add UI elements unless they help the user decide, act, avoid mistakes, or understand status.

Use shadcn/ui, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, lucide-react, and cn().
